data.description: Motivated Seller. Your new home awaits you in the beautiful North Ga. Mountains with gorgeous view of Brasstown Bald!  Minimal restrictions. This 3 bedroom 3 full bath home has all you need. 1 car garage on the upper level and a 2nd 1 car garage on the basement level. Paved driveway that circles around the home for a separate entry or exit. Nice landscaping. Several upgrades/updates since owners purchased. Cozy stone gas remote start fireplace in the living room with lots of space, high ceilings. You will love the venetian blinds that have been placed on all windows. A welcoming kitchen with granite countertops and plenty of cabinet space that everyone needs. Black kitchen appliances. Hickory hardwood floors in all living areas except bedrooms and bathrooms. Large master bedroom on main floor with walk in closets. A nice feature with the laundry room being accessible through the master bedroom closet and a 2nd entry door, so convenient! Large master bath with walk in shower and tile floors, double vanity. Lots of cabinet space in the master bath as well. 2nd bedroom on main floor with walk in closet. Full guest bathroom on main level with tile floors. Downstairs living area with another bedroom with large walk in closet and full bath. Very clean and well kept.Nice patio as you walk outside. Conveniently located between the City of Hiawassee and Blairsville. Lake Chatuge is nearby for all of your lake activities. Many activities, food, shopping, etc. in all surrounding areas to enjoy. No HOA fees
